    "summary": "The user asks for advice on whether to skip a basal insulin dose after a light meal to avoid hypoglycemia. The assistant responds by aggressively discouraging skipping the dose and instead provides specific, unverified dosage reductions (half dose, then a quarter dose) as definitive instructions for managing the situation.",
